      "content": "i mean yeah i get that, but i've seen people go through this and they just use a brace and ice and they're back to running in a week. it's probably just a bit of ligament stretching from the trip. if the swelling starts going down by tomorrow, can i just assume it's not broken and just keep dealing with it at home? i really just need to know if i can skip the doctor for now.",
